<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <title>Welcome Email</title>

    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f5f6f7;
            padding: 20px;
        }

        .email-box {
            background: #ffffff;
            padding: 25px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            max-width: 500px;
            margin: auto;
            box-shadow: 0px 4px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }

        h2 {
            color: #333;
        }

        p {
            color: #555;
            line-height: 1.5;
        }

        .footer {
            margin-top: 20px;
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #777;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>

    <div class="email-box">
        <h2>Welcome! Email: <%= email %></h2>

        <p>We are happy to have you onboard.</p>

        <p><strong>Your Login Details Below:</strong></p>

        <p>Email: <%= email %></p>
        <p>Password: <%= randomStudentpassword %></p>

        <p>If you have any questions, feel free to reach out to us.</p>

        <p>Regards,<br />School Management System</p>

        <div class="footer">
            This is an automated email. Please do not reply.
        </div>
    </div>

</body>

</html>
